headline: Can Nike Stock Reach $100 in 2025?
summary: Nike (NYSE: NKE) is proving that even some of the most dominant and well-known businesses can hit a rough patch.  Can this consumer discretionary stock reverse course, rise 33% from its current $75 price tag, and get to $100 in 2025?  Adidas is in second place with a 9% share, showcasing Nike's commanding lead of the industry.
